result.name: Saigon Pho

reviews.text: The food is pretty good for the price with a lot of variety. Service is really fast with good location
Friendly staff and the soup base is very tasty, and good price
Went for an early dinner after arriving back from a 15 hour flight. Menu has a good selection and we had the pho which was tasty. Good value for the money.
It's one of my go-to restaurants, with a relaxed atmosphere, affordable prices (compared to the other options in Sai Kung pier!), and good food. 😁
Big portions at great price
